725808f-a.title: Queens: 114th Street - 41st Avenue
725808f-a.text:
(1)
114th Street, south from 4lst Avenue. Cn the left
are the World's Fair groundsf1939-40)and Grand Central
Parkway.
P. L. Sperr  May 30, 1938
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(s)
Houses on 114th Street near 41st Avenue, and the
trylon of the 1939-40 World's Fair in Flushing Meadow
Park. The view is southwestward from Roosevelt Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  May 30, 1938
NO REPRODUCTIONS
